{"tid":2517844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加州迪士尼樂園「王子吻公主」一幕被指教壞細路 美媒：王子應獲得公主同意","createTime":"2021-05-05T14:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T14:43:23.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"098b87c712c28182af9d921b713688a91cfff8fb","tid":2517844,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"美國加州迪士尼樂園於上月底重新開放，白雪公主園區新設施「Snow White&rsquo;s Enchanted Wish」隨即惹來爭議。有外媒批評新設施重現「王子吻公主」一幕係教壞細路，認為王子趁公主昏迷嗰陣親吻對方，並唔係真愛嘅表現，我哋都教細路要兩情相悅先可以親吻對方。<br />\n<br />\n由於疫情問題，加州迪士尼樂園停業超過一年，為咗增加吸引力，迪士尼就喺閉園期間翻新白雪公主園區，增設新設施「Snow White&rsquo;s Enchanted Wish」，重現白雪公主故事場景，當中就包括「王子吻公主」經典一幕。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個舉動就引起外媒「SF Gate」編輯Katie Dowd及Julie Tremaine不滿，佢哋認為王子趁公主昏迷嗰陣親吻對方，唔係真愛嘅表現，並表示「我哋唔係都教小朋友，要雙方同意先可以錫對方嘅咩？我真係唔明，點解到咗2021年，仍然可以將男人對女人做咩都得嘅守舊想法加入園內。」<br />\n<br />\n其實近年迪士尼樂園都被人鬧過幾次，園內經典遊樂設施「Jungle Cruise（叢林巡航）」就曾被指涉嫌種族歧視，將原住民塑造成野蠻人同食人族。而另一個經典設施「Splash Mountain﹙飛濺山﹚」，由於概念源至一套被指「美化奴隸制」嘅電影《Song of the South（南方之歌）》而被鬧爆，最終迪士尼以黑人少女做主角嘅電影《The Princess and the Frog（公主與青蛙）》重新包裝嚟平息爭議。"},{"pid":"ca2086d6f5825cd151c845fd410252ac136d3041","tid":2517844,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:38:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=26699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dhobby%26aid%3D26699&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnx0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=f42809c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=26699</a>"},{"pid":"cb259010d420784ebd34ea2bbdff794705e49fd3","tid":2517844,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"以後迪士尼D戲會加入律師角色"},{"pid":"db3347f5200921fe1240e5cb33ba6fe00550e757","tid":2517844,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"正!<br />\n加速"},{"pid":"f67bf1a8a6cdb92d2c343579d484c3e682dd558e","tid":2517844,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"要加LGBT人獸元素<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15e8e485001fdc63e3b900bce09dab81ba47013","tid":2517844,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS3p8xFihvrU4yCfJo598fYhNWWudtbyEVcPp7bASFW6J?filename=RnS2Ygz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnS2Ygz.png&h=6123d38e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"88aebb6e3d753097b38a5fcb5da2568727ad0294","tid":2517844,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"做乜撚都係錯<br />\n美女與野獸玩人獸交啱曬佢哋"}]}